        "content": [
            "一行人在莱昂尼多契约龙的业火前败下阵来。\\n被卷入其中的沙音为报答救命之恩，\\n告诉了众人其被教会拯救的往事，\\n随后又试图回到莱昂尼多身边。\\n一行人认为不能坐视不管，追了上去。"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "追上了！\\n等等，莱昂尼多哥哥！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "嗯？又是你。\\n还要来纠缠我，真是愚蠢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100003_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "兰扎卜",
            "context": "在你解放魔神之前，先揍飞再说！\\n做好觉悟吧！嘿呀！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "要做好觉悟的是你！\\n一闪即灭！哈啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不会让你攻击阁下。\\n这都是为了夺回从前的生活！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "士兵们，给我上！\\n别让这些人活着回去！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国军",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "纳姆",
            "context": "既然如此，我们也要使出全力了！\\n大家上啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "各位，摆好阵形！\\n准备迎击！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，真是凄惨。\\n如同一群无力的蝼蚁……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_02"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我这就把你们收拾干净。\\n出来吧，我的契约龙玛斯！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不好！这家伙是打算\\n连自己人都一起干掉吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "不过，区区焰龙之炎，\\n就让我以身挡下……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "就凭你吗，小丫头！\\n唔噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "咕噢噢噢噢噢噢噢噢！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这、这家伙！？不是玛斯！？\\n可是这魔力毫无疑问是焰龙的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "难道你，\\n被人类夺去了身体！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "哼，说夺去身体也太难听了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我和这家伙缔结契约，\\n还帮他达成了心愿。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "给他接上了大量魔导管，\\n实现了他成为世界上最强火龙的愿望！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "把龙用作炼金术的试验品！？\\n你这家伙……\\n把龙当成什么了！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "好了，让你们尝尝融入了人类智慧\\n从而获得新生的龙之火焰吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "魔力炮装填！魔导效果加乘，\\n龙炎临界点突破，连锁释放！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100013_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "消失吧，蝼蚁们！\\n炼金爆弹！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "200009_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "玛斯",
            "context": "咕噢啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "这种攻击，根本挡不住啊！\\n大家快逃！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "全员",
            "context": "哇啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "真是无趣……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "呵呵呵，我之前不是说了么，沙音？\\n“你的殒命之处不在这里”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "我帮你准备了最适合你的死法。\\n辛苦你把敌人引过来了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "莱昂尼多",
            "context": "为了表彰你的功绩，我会保护教会的。\\n呵呵……哈哈哈哈！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "大、大家都没事吗！？\\n振作点，站得起来吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "唔、嗯……\\n多亏了穆穆，勉强保住一命……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_1001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "似乎削弱了一些火焰的威力。\\n不过……对不起，亲爱的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_08"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "要是我能把那家伙的火焰\\n全都挡下来的话……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "呜、嘶……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_04"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "咦！？\\n这家伙居然还活着！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "快离开他，\\n尤蒂尔！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "没事，他这个样子不能把我怎么样。\\n沙音，你还好吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "你……想干嘛……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不论立场如何，\\n我都不能丢下受伤的人不管。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "来，\\n抓住我的肩膀……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "住、住手……\\n别随随便便碰我……\\n啊！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "咦？这个体型！？\\n难道你是……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "是个女人……还真是抱歉了啊……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "不，对不起！\\n因为你平时说话的语气，\\n我还以为……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "库菈乌，总之你先帮她治疗吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_1003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "沙音，你和埃尔菲莉丝之间\\n到底……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "听你们的对话，不像是单纯的敌对关系。\\n是以前有过什么……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "尤蒂尔，我来说吧……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "不，让我自己说。\\n也算是对救命之恩的一点回报。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我曾经\\n是个无家可归的孩子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "每天过着流落街头的生活。\\n是埃尔菲莉丝救了我。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "她把我带去了……伊莉雅教会。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "对于吃了上顿没下顿的我来说，\\n那里就是乐园。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "我在教会……懂得了什么是爱。\\n然后我暗自发誓。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "只要不幸的孩子不再出现，\\n为了保护这里，我什么都愿意做。\\n",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "那你为什么\\n会成为暗杀者……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "因为出现了企图破坏乐园的家伙。\\n而且是教会内部出现的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "魔神是伊莉雅的孩子。\\n教会中出现了不遵从新教义的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0062",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_12"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "你是说……炼狱文书吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0063",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "没错。主教大人明明向我们宣告\\n要连魔神一并去爱，为什么他们不认同？\\n为什么要分裂教会？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0064",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "所以我决定，要用流落街头时\\n磨炼出的本领制裁破坏乐园的家伙。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0065",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "惩罚不知悔改者，\\n接纳愿意悔过者。如此一来……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0066",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "教会又会恢复团结。\\n那么……埃尔菲莉丝也……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0067",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100002_11"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "埃尔菲莉丝",
            "context": "沙音……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_0068",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100005_06"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "沙音",
            "context": "所以我不会认同那些叛徒，\\n也不会认同帮助他们的你们。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_MAINSTORY_08_05_1002",
